Number = {3},
Month = {SEP},
Abstract = {The rapid advancement of genitive AI, like Chat- GPT, has initiated a
   profound transformation in higher education. It offers customized
   learning experiences, automates administrative tasks, and provides
   personalized support to students and educators. Following PRISMA
   guidelines, this paper presents systematic review that delives into the
   implications of genitive Al Al, a cutting-edge language model, ,in
   higher education. We adopted ChatGPT as an example of this study. It
   thoroughly examines the potential advantages and constraints of integrat
   ing ChatGPT into educational Avironments, assessing the quality of 35
   selected articles and conducting a comprehensive meta-analysis of their
   findings. This study yields fresh insights into the multifaceted
   consequencestof employing ChatGPT in higher education and underscores
   the intricate landscape asso- ciated with Al integration in academic
   settings. It It emphasizes the imperativeness of addressing ethical,
   legal, and pragmatic challenges while capitalizing on the potential
   benefits of Al technology in education. Our systematic review reveals a
   consistent reservation trend regarding generative Al integration within
   educational contexts. These concerhs encompass many issues, emphasizing
   the necessity for judicibus implementation and robust safeguards to
   mitigate potential challenges.},
